arrogance was his weakness

14
00:00:40,049 --> 00:00:43,229
and he played to that weakness like a strategic poker player.

15
00:00:43,229 --> 00:00:47,019
Not showing his true feelings toward the emperor, Talleyrand bided his time,

16
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:50,760
made the right connections, which helped create the most elaborate scheme to

17
