infamous people, Napolean Bonaparte.
These are some strategies to keep in

19
00:00:56,829 --> 00:00:58,500
mind during war times.

20
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:03,539
Reacting rather than directing. Keep others reacting to your moves, keep them

21
