on the defensive.

22
00:01:04,709 --> 00:01:08,349
Play to their ineffectiveness to stay calm. Aggression

23
00:01:08,349 --> 00:01:13,109
versus effective action. Don’t waste a lot of energy trying to make your point,

24
00:01:13,109 --> 00:01:16,599
bide your time like Talleyrand. Make the other person come to you,

