37
00:01:55,728 --> 00:01:58,798
Now, 5 Benefits to making your opponents come to you

38
00:01:58,799 --> 00:02:02,409
It is a wise thing to lure your opponent on hostile ground;

39
00:02:02,409 --> 00:02:05,310
it is a subtle way to put him on the defensive.

40
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:09,030
Your opponent will be nervous which will cause him to rush his actions and make

41
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:09,819
mistakes.

42
00:02:09,819 --> 00:02:13,370
You want to create the illusion that your opponent is in control of the

43
00:02:13,370 --> 00:02:14,150
situation.

44
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:18,150
Oftentimes, your opponent’s greed, desires and emotions will be their great

45
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:21,960
motivator which means that they can be easily led around and/or defeated.

46
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:25,900
Getting people to dig their own graves forces their hand and makes you appear

47
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:28,000
powerful and demand respect.

48
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:31,300
Now, is there ever a good time to go to your opponent, you ask?

49
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:34,469
Yes, of course there is an exception to the rule when you should go to your

50
00:02:34,469 --> 00:02:34,979
opponent.

51
00:02:34,979 --> 00:02:38,409
Depending on the situation, bait and wait is a wise choice

52
00:02:38,409 --> 00:02:41,629
but taking the lead to attack your opponent can be advantageous

53
00:02:41,629 --> 00:02:45,250
as well. The element of surprise does not give the opponent time to think of a

54
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:46,169
counter attack.

55
00:02:46,169 --> 00:02:49,329
They are left at your mercy and must respond to your terms.

56
00:02:49,330 --> 00:02:52,890
Your biggest issue is to know what tactic to use and the right time to use it

57
00:02:53,129 --> 00:02:56,699
To bait and wait or to strike with force, that is the dilemma.

58
00:02:56,699 --> 00:02:59,839
You can be like the bear hunter who lays the honey bait trap.

59
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:02,860
He doesn’t exhaust himself and risk his life to find the bear

60
